     "{\"template\":\"intro\",\"texts\":[\"Pensions from the TfL Pension Fund increase in April 2018.\"],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "This is based on the rise in the Retail Price Index over the 12 months to September 2017 which was 3.9%.",
     "Depending on the period of membership of the TfL Pension Fund, your pension may comprise of various components, some of which are not increased by the Fund at the above rate, but may be increased by the State.",
     "If you have been receiving your pension for less than a year you may receive a pro rata increase, as shown in the table.",
